\fs22 In December 1998, scientists at Dubna ({\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Joint_Institute_for_Nuclear_Research"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 Joint Institute for Nuclear Research}}) in Russia bombarded a 
\fs18 \super 244
